        "content": [
            "被困的守护龙希尔维亚\\n疑似发生异变……\\n王子和梅露莎很担心她的安危，\\n此时强敌暴风石挡在了他们面前。\\n为尽快赶往村落，王子等人决定正面突破。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "看招！\\n嘿啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "搞定！\\n好！下一个对手在哪里！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "希里丝那家伙，\\n真有两下子啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是的，本领真是了得。\\n说不定比卢卡更强？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂喂！？可别说笑！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我认同她的弓箭水平，\\n但她的战斗方式还是让人捏把汗啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "只顾看眼前，\\n要是被偷袭……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶！？从侧面来！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "还没说完就来了！\\n这里就看我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "希里丝！你没事吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "梅露莎！\\n谢谢你！得救了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那个叫梅露莎的小姑娘，\\n观察周围很仔细啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "虽然胆子有点小，\\n但在战场上，这样才能活得久。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "跟勇猛果断的希里丝\\n是一对好搭档呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嘿啊！\\n往你那边去了，梅露莎！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "好，别想跑！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "哎呀？怎么了，卢卡？\\n一脸沉闷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哈哈，是感到寂寞了吧。\\n她不再需要哥哥的帮助了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "妹妹能独当一面了，\\n你应该为她高兴啊……对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "才、才没有觉得寂寞！\\n而且她哪有独当一面？\\n靠着梅露莎的力量只能算是个半吊子！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不过……也是啊。\\n那家伙，交到了一个好朋友呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这一点，我也很高兴。\\n太好了……希里丝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好。所有魔兽都清理完毕了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "呼……好可怕……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "梅露莎，你没事吧？\\n你说过不怎么喜欢打斗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "连续交战，你累坏了吧？\\n在附近休息一下吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "不……这点程度我没事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "就快到我的村落了，\\n请让我继续带路吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "王子与梅露莎等人马不停蹄地赶路。\\n途中……一行人来到了\\n梅露莎与希尔维亚的回忆之地。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "哇～景色一览无余！\\n居然有这么美的地方！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "这里是希尔维亚中意的地方，\\n我也经常来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "希尔维亚是热爱自然、\\n性格沉稳的龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "靠在希尔维亚身上，感受着微风\\n拂过脸颊，仰望缓缓流动的云朵……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "这般舒缓柔和的悠闲时光，\\n是我的宝物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "太好了……\\n这里似乎还没有被帝国军占领……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "那我就继续带路吧，\\n前往村落……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "梅露莎……\\n在那里的，是梅露莎吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "咦！？这个声音……希尔维亚！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "果然是希尔维亚！\\n太好了！你逃出来了啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希尔维亚",
            "context": "不……这只是我的意识，\\n没有实体，如幻象一般。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希尔维亚",
            "context": "能像这样与你交谈的时间，\\n已经所剩无几。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希尔维亚",
            "context": "有一句话……\\n我必须告诉你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希尔维亚",
            "context": "不可以……来救我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "诶……什么意思？\\n我是为了你才……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希尔维亚",
            "context": "尤蒂尔……\\n拥有龙之力的王子啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希尔维亚",
            "context": "啊，我已经……到了极限……\\n请带着梅露莎逃离这里……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "希尔维亚！？\\n等等，希尔维亚！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "消、消失了！？\\n尤蒂尔，这是怎么回事！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我也不清楚……\\n但有种不祥的预感。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "对，或许该加快脚步了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "怎么会这样……\\n难道希尔维亚出了什么事！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "呜……希尔维亚！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊！等等，梅露莎！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "梅露莎！\\n太好了……追上你了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "嗯！？殿下，等等！\\n那魔兽到底是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "是帝国军的手下！\\n连希尔维亚也敌不过的魔兽之一！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶！？那不是很强吗！？\\n怎、怎么办！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "它的行动很有规律……\\n看起来像是在既定路线上巡逻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "要是能趁其不备，\\n从它身后溜过去就好了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "没那么容易吧。\\n马上会被它发现，然后受到攻击。\\n该怎么办好呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我要战斗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "咦……梅露莎？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "打倒它，然后前进！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "这条路是通往村落……\\n是解救希尔维亚的捷径！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "梅露莎……这么拼命……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "知道了！\\n我跟你一起战斗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "希里丝……\\n嗯！谢谢你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20402_03_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
